CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: New Found Gold Corp is a mineral exploration company engaged in the acquisition, exploration and evaluation of resource properties with a focus on gold properties located in the Provinces of Newfoundland and Labrador and Ontario, Canada. Its principal objective is to explore and develop the Queensway Project, which is located near Gander, Newfoundland.
